    "note": "Design-first artifact only \u2014 describes the MCP tool surface, not a running server. Tool input/output schemas $ref the same object schemas as the OpenAPI; each tool maps to an OpenAPI operationId. Fronts the DOB legacy application layer (BIS Web, DOB NOW, eFiling) and its nightly Socrata batch dump with one agent contract, and adds the net-new write workflow: filing a DOB NOW permit application.",
